---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavH from '../components/NavH.astro';
import HeroH from '../components/HeroH.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Timeline from '../components/Timeline.astro';
import TimelineItem from '../components/TimelineItem.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Gallery from '../components/Gallery.astro';
---

<Layout title="Gwyn Tangog">
  <NavH />
  <HeroH />

  <Section id="VisualArts" eyebrow="" title="&#9998 Traditional Art">
    <p>I started out overwhelmed by colors, so I started by taking traditional graphite pencil lessons online! &#128221</p>

      <Gallery images={[
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/broken_tree.jpeg`, alt: "Inspired by an image I saw, and it me back into drawing!"},
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/pencil_snail.jpeg`, alt: "Snail"},
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/spotted_snake_desk.jpeg`, alt: "I like snakes."},
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/colored_flowers.jpeg`, alt: "Flowers"},
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/colored_fruits.jpeg`, alt: "Fruits"},
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/flower_vase.jpeg`, alt: "Flowers (again?)"},
        {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/trad_art/solid_snake.jpeg`, alt: "I really like snakes."},
      ]} />

  </Section>



  <Section id="DigitalArts" eyebrow="" title="&#128396 Digital Art">
    <p>I got inspired by an art trend going around on YouTube where artists would draw their favorite
    characters in their style. That was my first digital project! </p>

    <Gallery images={[
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/digital_art/motivational_gwyn.png`, alt: "Mini mascot of myself."},
      {video: 'https://youtube.com/shorts/-MMRN1MKxKI?feature=share', alt: "My take on the Sienna art trend."},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/digital_art/shuppet.jpeg`, alt: "Shuppet"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/digital_art/phantump.jpeg`, alt: "Phantump"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/digital_art/card.jpeg`, alt: "A Pokemon card of myself!"},
    ]} />

  </Section>

   <Section id="Crochet" eyebrow="" title="&#x1F9F6 Crochet">
    <p>Got back into it after a few years since I wanted to make a plushie of my mochi
    character. &#x1F361 I like soft things.</p>

    <Gallery images={[
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/crochet/crochet_mochi_2.jpeg`, alt: "One determined little mochi."},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/crochet/crochet_bunny.jpeg`, alt: "Bunny in overalls!"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/crochet/crochet_turtles.jpeg`, alt: "Flower turtles!"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/crochet/crochet_bears.jpeg`, alt: "My big bear, and a smaller bear that I was commissioned to make for a baby."},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/crochet/crochet_beanie.jpeg`, alt: "A cat beanie with a crescent moon on it."},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/crochet/crochet_cats.jpeg`, alt: "Little crochet cats!"},
    ]} />

  </Section>

   <Section id="Pokemon Cards" eyebrow="" title="&#127922 Pokemon Cards">
    <p>I started out collecting the cards a few months ago, then got into the game shortly after.
    I enjoy strategy games, and this reminds me of being excited to play chess after school in
    elementary school. &#x1F389; I collect full arts of steel types and ghost types, and I currently
    play two different decks: Dragapult &#x1F432 &#128053 and Mega Venusaur  &#x1F33F &#x2600;&#xFE0F.</p>

   <Gallery images={[
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/pokemon/mega_venusaur.jpeg`, alt: "Jungle dump!"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/pokemon/dragapult_dusk.jpeg`, alt: "Phantom Dive!"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/pokemon/Lyn_michi.jpeg`, alt: "Michi method binder for my sister."},
    ]} />

  </Section>

  <Section id="Music" eyebrow="" title="&#127908 Music">
    <p>Even though I really wanted to sing, I learned to play fingerstyle guitar because I was insecure of my voice.
    Over time, I overcame the insecurity, and I have performed as vocalist and guitarist multiple times!</p>

    <Gallery images={[
      {video: 'https://youtu.be/fsFrOO7gnws', alt: "Ghost of You", caption: "Ghost of You"},
      {video: 'https://youtu.be/C-I3s_9D1g0', alt: "Message in a Bottle", caption: "Message in a Bottle"},
    ]} />

  </Section>

   <Section id="Others" eyebrow="" title="&#9823 Others">
    <p>I also like playing video games and writing poetry, but there aren't any interesting pictures for those.</p>

  <Gallery images={[
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/others/monopoly.jpeg`, alt: "Monopoly --- won the capitalism simulation game."},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/others/chinese_checkers.jpeg`, alt: "Chinese checkers --- taught my friends to play!"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/others/chess.jpeg`, alt: "Chess --- a hilarious game with a great player. He turned all his pawns to horses."},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/others/yellow_flowers.jpeg`, alt: "An origami gift I made!"},
      {src: `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/others/big_origami.jpeg`, alt: "Giant origami..."},
    ]} />

  </Section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .hobby-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }
</style>
